'''Afgan''' ([[Assaɣ ussnan]]: ''Homo sapiens'')  d [[amuddir]] amyiwen id yegran seg [[afgan amasnag|ufgan amasnag]] deg [[tawsit (tudersent)|tewsit]] n [[Humu]] (ifganen), Afgan d [[Aseklu n temhazt n tdefrin|angaz]] deg [[taɣreft (Tasartut)|teɣreft]] n [[Izunefganen]] yeṭṭafaren [[tawacult (tasnudert)|tawacult]] n [[tifganyin]], Afgan d amuddir amyiwen iy lan (yesɛan) [[allaɣ]] yenneflin s waṭas, iy zemren ad [[Asekti|issekti]] w ad issexdem [[tutlayt]] w ad yaf tifrat i wuguren id yettmagar, Yerna [[tafekka|tafekka-ynes]] tbedd s ijufaṛ [[Tawremt|iwermanen]] ifellayen d iddayen issifrar awliwel-is (issisehil aḥerrk-is) s tenmeẓla d [[allaɣ|wallaɣ]] dɣa anecta d ayla yettgin deg ufgan d amuddir amyiwen iy zemren ad yessexdem tizmmarin-is [[agerru|tiggerruyin]] d [[tafekka|tfekkawin]] d usexdem n [[Afus|ufus]] akken igerrez i tmugri d isnulfu n ifecka i yesri (i yuḥwaj) deg tudert-is, Akken ila (yesɛa) taɣect d tukrist sgi iy ttmeslay.

Tiɣri n [[timesɣezt|timesɣaz]] tesseken-d anza d akken afgan yella deg [[Tafriqt|Tefrikt]] send n 300.000 n iseggasen maca tura yettidir deg [[Amenẓaw|imenẓawen]] n [[tagnit|tegnit]] s wuṭṭunyugaren 7,3 n imelyaren n ifganen 

Afgan am yakk [[tigjdanin]] tiflalin d amuddir amettan.

== Aẓaṛ nufgan d tnekra-ynes ==
'''Deg usɣan'''
Wid yettamnen s [[Ajjed|isɣanen]] ttamnen d akken [[yillu]] isnulfa-d (ixelqed) afgan deg tugna-ynes tamirant deg yiwet n [[tasint|tsint]], Maca [[Timesɣezt|timesɣaz]] qqaren-t-d s temhazt deg 200.000 n iseggasen i wayen umi qqaren imusnawen [[Humu]] dah n [[Tamhazt|tiẓri n temhazt]] deg wakud dgi ttwalin imusnawen n usɣan inselmen d akken yerra fellasen yisem n ''Bashar- بشر'' acku ttwalin d akken afgan amiran yusad seg [[Adem]] igan d bab n ifganen yakk.

'''Deg tasnudert'''
Imusnawen qqaren-d d akken ''Australopithecus afarensis'' d yiwen n umraw n ifganen ([[Angar|yenger]]) i yellan iteddu s sin n iṭarren, Allaɣ-is yella meẓẓiy s tmuɣli ar wagla n ufgan amiran.

